<p>For so many people, 2023 was the year of empathic distress&#8212;the pain of feeling others&#8217; pain, while feeling helpless to do anything about it. To kick off 2024, I <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/01/01/opinion/israel-war-empathy-pain.html">wrote about</a> why empathy often drains and restrains us, and how compassion can help. </p><p>The most basic form of compassion is not assuaging distress but acknowledging it. Even if you can&#8217;t make people feel better, you can still help them feel seen.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/01/01/opinion/israel-war-empathy-pain.html" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5253922e-4845-4c51-a78e-417dbcd09fff_794x1094.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5253922e-4845-4c51-a78e-417dbcd09fff_794x1094.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5253922e-4845-4c51-a78e-417dbcd09fff_794x1094.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5253922e-4845-4c51-a78e-417dbcd09fff_794x1094.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5253922e-4845-4c51-a78e-417dbcd09fff_794x1094.jpeg" width="342" height="471.2191435768262" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack